@startuml 01-sequence-admin-oauth-flow
' wave-c-supabase-rls-auth — Admin OAuth Flow (Sequence Diagram)
' Source of truth: openspec/changes/wave-c-supabase-rls-auth/design.md §4

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 8
skinparam defaultFontName "Sans-Serif"
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.4

skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFAEC
  ParticipantBorderColor     #6B5638
  ActorBackgroundColor       #ECE0C4
  ActorBorderColor           #2A1F12
  LifeLineBackgroundColor    #D9C9A4
  LifeLineBorderColor        #6B5638
  GroupBackgroundColor       #F8F1E0
  GroupBorderColor           #6B5638
}

actor "Yuki\n(admin candidate)" as user
participant "Browser" as browser
participant "/admin/login\n(Client Component)" as loginPage
participant "Supabase Auth\n(OAuth handler)" as supaAuth
participant "github.com\n(OAuth consent)" as github
participant "middleware.ts\n(Edge)" as mw
participant "/admin/upload\n(protected)" as uploadPage
participant "/ (home)\n(flash toast handler)" as home

== 1. 進入登入頁 ==
user -> browser: 點「Admin 登入」連結
browser -> loginPage: GET /admin/login
note right of mw
  middleware bypass：
  pathname === "/admin/login"
  → NextResponse.next()
end note
loginPage --> browser: render Card + GitHub OAuth Button

== 2. 觸發 OAuth ==
user -> browser: 按下「以 GitHub 登入」
browser -> supaAuth: signInWithOAuth\n({ provider: 'github',\n   redirectTo: <origin>/admin/upload })
supaAuth --> browser: 302 → github.com/login/oauth/authorize

== 3. GitHub 同意授權 ==
browser -> github: GET /login/oauth/authorize
user -> github: 確認授權
github --> browser: 302 → supabase.co/auth/v1/callback?code=...

== 4. Supabase callback 換 session ==
browser -> supaAuth: GET /auth/v1/callback?code=...
supaAuth -> github: POST /login/oauth/access_token
github --> supaAuth: access_token + user_metadata.user_name
supaAuth --> browser: Set-Cookie: sb-<ref>-auth-token\n302 → /admin/upload

== 5. middleware 比對 admin ==
browser -> mw: GET /admin/upload\n(Cookie: sb-<ref>-auth-token)
mw -> supaAuth: getUser(session)
supaAuth --> mw: { user_metadata: { user_name } }

alt user_name === ADMIN_GITHUB_USERNAME (放行)
  mw --> browser: NextResponse.next()
  browser -> uploadPage: render protected route
  uploadPage --> browser: 「Coming soon · GPX 上傳開發中」+ Sign out button

else user_name !== ADMIN_GITHUB_USERNAME (擋下)
  mw -> supaAuth: signOut()
  supaAuth --> mw: ok (cookie cleared)
  mw --> browser: 302 → /?auth_error=not_admin
  browser -> home: GET /?auth_error=not_admin
  home --> browser: render home + sonner toast「您不是 admin，已登出」\n+ router.replace('/') 清 query
end

== 6. (選用) Sign out ==
user -> browser: 按「Sign out」
browser -> supaAuth: signOut()
supaAuth --> browser: cookie cleared, 302 → /

@enduml
